The base swerve controller assumes counter clockwise is positive.  If the navx2 is plugged into the Rio and rightside up, you will need to invert the gyro. In that configuration the gyro is clockwise positive.

In the swerve.java file

After installing the vendor dependency delete line 11 add: import com.kauailabs.navx.frc.AHRS; import edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.SPI;

Delete line 24 Add private final AHRS gyro;

Delete line 27-28 Add gyro = new AHRS(SPI.Port.kMXP);

Then change the boolean in constants.java

public static final boolean invertGyro = true;
